author: skitching
msg: Refactor pattern-parsing into two phases: first split it into a list of formatter and literal segments, then iterate over the list to perform the parse or format. This allows one formatter to vary depending on what other formatters are present, which is unfortunately necessary for ww/yyyy pattern support (bad java.text.SimpleDateFormat design).
